plot: Biscuit announces to Gon and Killua that she will be their teacher.

Binolt all attacks Biscuit, she easily defeats him. Gon and Killua seeing her strength asked her to be their master and proceed to fight Binolt for 6 days. He gives up and they let him go. They go to the city of Masadora and got some cards but told them to go back to the rocky area again. Biscuit tells them that they are going exactly straight to Masadora but this time, they have to dig through the rocks, whilst doing so they discover another part of Ten, Shu.—paulp1988
